10. Risk Mitigation & Data Quality Watchpoints

Disability Mapping The existing Excel Disability column is inconsistent. Import is blocked until manual value-mapping aligns Excel data with DART enum values (e.g., cognitive, physical, multiple, visual).

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Sync Conflicts (HTTP 409) If two facilitators record the same session offline, the server will return an HTTP 409 Conflict upon sync. The frontend must catch this and prompt the user to resolve overlapping entries manually to ensure data integrity.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Duplicate Beneficiaries In the event of duplicate UUIDs during offline registration, the server will flag the record for administrator review rather than auto-merging data.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Unassigned Facilitators Facilitators without an active user_location_assignment will be blocked from the attendance screen to prevent orphaned data. Peter will see a clear error: "You are not assigned to a CFS location. Contact your administrator."